partnerDetails.about: Springs Bee Gee Electrical Wholesalers are electrical wholesales situated in Second Street in the Springs CBD. They are major distributors of leading imported and local brands to large corporations and parastatals. Cliff Carr and Derek Waters, both born and schooled in Springs, established the business in the early ’80s from humble beginnings in 12th Street, later moving to small premises in New Era.
